of two numbers.

00:00:21.528 --> 00:00:22.466
One way to think about them

00:00:22.466 --> 00:00:25.328
is if I were to find, say,
the least common multiple

00:00:25.328 --> 00:00:29.763
between, I don't know, four and six,

00:00:29.763 --> 00:00:31.325
you literally could look
at all the multiples

00:00:31.325 --> 00:00:33.876
