00:00:49.647 --> 00:00:52.562
they'll actually have
multiple common multiples,

00:00:52.562 --> 00:00:55.018
but the least of the common multiples

00:00:55.018 --> 00:00:59.109
you immediately see is going to be 12.

00:00:59.109 --> 00:01:00.761
Now another way to think about it

00:01:00.761 --> 00:01:03.603
